    public class SpringBootPropsGen
extends java.lang.Object
implements RunnableApp
    Run this class redirecting stdout to config/application.properties to generate the file. This way we can keep all config data in Java and avoid common issues. 
     java -jar build/libs/ome-smuggler-*.jar ome.smuggler.run.SpringBootPropsGen \
  > src/main/resources/config/application.properties
